//Definintions
Rest - Representational State Transfer

Resource - Single item (object) in a database
    /user

Collection - A Collection of similar items in a database
    /users

Base(root) url - http://amazon.com/

API endpoint - http://amazon.com/movies

Parameters - /movies/:movieId

Query (query stream) - /movies?genre=action&year=1999

Clients - front end, website, interacting

Server - Intermediary, recieves request and passing to cient 

Request Methods - for most inportant GET PUT POST DELETE